<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Ascend" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Ascend,</orth> to mount, climb, 1) trans.: <cit><quote>a. her chamber-window,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 3.1.39" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. III, 1, 39</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.3.147" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 3, 147</bibl>. <cit><quote>my chambers,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.3.173" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 3, 173</bibl></cit>. <emph>they</emph> (curses) <cit><quote>a. the sky,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.287" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 287</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a. the brightest heaven of invention,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.287" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 287</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a. the throne,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 4.111" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 IV, 111</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. r2 4.111" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 IV, 111</bibl> <bibl n="shak. r2 5.1.56" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 56</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 3.1.71" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B III, 1, 71</bibl>. <cit><quote>Pantheon,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 1.333" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. I, 333</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) intr. to rise: <cit><quote>peace a. to heaven,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jn 2.86" default="NO" valid="yes">John II, 86</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>it --s me into the brain,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 4.3.105" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B IV, 3, 105</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a., brave Talbot,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.1.28" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 1, 28</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the base degrees by which he did a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. jc 2.1.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. II, 1, 27</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the noble Brutus is --ed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jc 3.2.11" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 11</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the dust should have --ed to the roof of heaven,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 3.6.49" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 6, 49</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>